reviewText: Great comedy from start to finish. Subject matter very insightful and entertaining ! A must see comedy routine ! Jokes are fresh and to the point !
Title: Alonzo Bodden: Who's Paying Attention?

reviewText: This hilarious special is perfect for times whenever you feel like laughing  at the weird stuff of this world we are living in and whenever you're looking to put a smile on your face. Alonzo is a comedy genius and is completely incredible in his timing and delivery! Highly recommended for any fan of stand up or comedy in general! One word: Funny.
Title: Alonzo Bodden: Who's Paying Attention?

Title: Alonzo Bodden: Who's Paying Attention?

reviewText: It's funny and witty.  It's intelligent humor, but not fall-down funny.  Not much more to add.  I think this comic works Vegas now.
Title: Alonzo Bodden: Who's Paying Attention?

reviewText: This guy is funny. The best I've seen in years. That said, I bought this after having seeing his Showtime special and was expecting 100% different material (this predated the special). Wasn't to be. At least, 1/3 is repeated monologue. Even so there a lot of laughs for your money.
Title: Alonzo Bodden: Who's Paying Attention?

reviewText: He's funny.  And he has really big hands.  So, who's paying attention?  Me.  My guess is, if he shot this show today, some of his jokes would need to be adjusted...like his health care joke.  Watch it, you'll understand.
Title: Alonzo Bodden: Who's Paying Attention?

reviewText: A fantastic,smart,funny,and wonderful stand-up who pays attention to detail and really makes you laugh at home. He is so good that when I asked my wife if we should turn off the dvd so we could  to watch "law and Order" she said  "No" "lets watch all of Alonzo Bodden. She is not into comedy but really enjoyed Mr. Bodden on stage. He is fantastic!!
summary: A smart funny and wonderful comedian who does a fantastic stand up.It's worth every penny to watch and listen to him!
Title: Alonzo Bodden: Who's Paying Attention?

reviewText: Alonzo is good here, covering a lot of topics with lots of laughs. I would also recommend 'Tall, Dark, and Funny', it was good, too.
Title: Alonzo Bodden: Who's Paying Attention?

reviewText: This was actually a funny DVD. The comedy was good without being raunchy. There were also a lot of references to current events, which was nice.
Title: Alonzo Bodden: Who's Paying Attention?
